Kaggle Notebooks (Training + Inference References)
YOLOv8 Training (Fine-tuning for PPE Detection)
- https://www.kaggle.com/code/hinepo/yolov8-finetuning-for-ppe-detection
Use: Shows how to fine-tune YOLOv8 on a PPE dataset (training setup, config, metrics, saving weights).

YOLOv8 Inference + Application Logic (Red Zone)
- https://www.kaggle.com/code/hinepo/yolov8-inference-for-red-zone-application
Use: Shows how to run inference with trained YOLOv8 weights and apply rule-based logic (ex: zones/violations) on detections.
